com.bobman159.rundml.core.sql.impl

Class CaseClause

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bobman159.rundml.core.sql.impl.CaseClause
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICaseClause, ISQLClause

    public class CaseClause
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICaseClause
    Defines a CASE expression WHEN expression THEN expression ... clause. Math and String operations are supported for the CASE but type checking is done by the DBMS and not by rundml2.0. Condition operations IE COLNOTNULLCHAR = 'Abc' are NOT currently supported use
